Revision history for Text-ASCIIPipe

1.001000
	- support optional handle for hooks (lets you plug in an object, for example)
	- add prefilter hook
	- rework hook call logic to ensure begin/end hooks being called, even for empty files

1.000001 (02.10.2012)
	Small documentation fixes.

1.000000 (01.10.2012)
	First release under new name (used to be called TextData::Piper in my private realm).

